{
  "stem": "322.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's what led me even back to Auschwitz in  '67 to revisit Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And since then, I lost track already how many times I went back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because that's the main purpose, in fact, from what I understand, knowing my colleagues who lived through that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They are anxious to know why did it have to happen?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When did you come to the United States?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I arrived August the 31st, 1946.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All alone, oh yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Alone.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was-- well, I arrived alone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, an uncle of mine, my mother's brother, who came to this country before I was even born, found my name in one of the Jewish organizations, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the-- I think it was the United-- one of the Jewish organizations.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was a roster there of Jews liberated in different camps.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And since I was liberated in Buchenwald, he says, Mermelstein, that's my sister's son.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm going to get him out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, he went, but he couldn't really bring that about on his own.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The affidavit was supplied by a Jewish organization, yeah, by the joint distribution committee.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that's how I arrived.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When I arrived, he was waiting for me at the boat, yeah, he and his wife, his son, his brother-in-law, and whatever else.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, and then there was the question of where would I go?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were also-- because the Red Cross, because if you are under 21, they had responsibility, you know, to see that you are well-kept.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Do you remember what ship you came on?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, the SS it was called.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "SS P-E-R-C-H.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a troop carrier, soldiers coming back from Europe.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so he took me, and he said that you'll live with me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then I remember even the scene.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
